    "persona_panel": "AI Persona ọrọ sisọ pẹpẹ - engage ninu authentic conversations pẹlu historical figures, scientists, literary oluyaworan, tabi tirẹ personas. Uses si ti ni ilọsiwaju AI si simulate period-accurate speech patterns, knowledge, ati perspectives. Perfect fun primary orisun analysis, perspective-taking, ati empathy-building exercises. atilẹyin ọ̀pọ̀lọpọ̀ response ọna: Ninu-oluyaworan (fully kíkún), Educational (pẹlu kíkọ́ scaffolds), tabi Mixed (balanced approach).",
    "persona_card": "AI persona ready fun conversation. kọọkan kaadi fihan oluyaworan's name, time period, ati expertise agbegbe. Tẹ si bẹrẹ interview - AI yoo respond authentically ti o da lori lori their historical context, beliefs, ati knowledge. Lo personas fun primary orisun analysis, perspective-taking exercises, tabi creative writing inspiration.",
    "persona_generate_button": "Ṣẹda AI personas automatically lati rẹ orisun akoonu. eto analyzes rẹ ọrọ si identify key figures, historical periods, tabi oluyaworan archetypes ati ṣẹda authentic conversational partners. Generated personas fikun accurate biographical awọn alaye, period-appropriate awọn ọrọ, ati contextual knowledge limitations (they won't know about events after their time).",
    "persona_select_button": "Yan eyi persona si begin rẹ interview tabi conversation. Once ti yan, iwọ'll wọle kíkún ọrọ sisọ interface ibi ti iwọ le ask ibeere, wadii their perspective, ati earn XP fun meaningful exchanges. AI responds ti o da lori lori oluyaworan's historical knowledge, personality, ati cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return si persona selection screen si yan different oluyaworan. rẹ current conversation ilọsiwaju jẹ automatically ti pamọ, ati iwọ le return si tẹsiwaju it later. eyi allows exploring ọ̀pọ̀lọpọ̀ perspectives lori same historical topic.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Fikun pato requirements fun bawo persona should behave during conversations. apẹẹrẹ: focus lori pato time period, emphasize certain beliefs tabi iye, maintain particular speech patterns, tabi limit responses si historically accurate knowledge. olukọ le lo eyi si align personas pẹlu pato kíkọ́ objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Yan bawo persona responds si ṣẹda different kíkọ́ àwọn ìrírí. IN oluyaworan: Fully kíkún historical ohun pẹlu no ìpòsírn explanations. EDUCATIONAL: oluyaworan speaks ṣugbọn pẹlu kíkọ́ scaffolds, awọn ọrọ atilẹyin, ati context. MIXED: Balanced approach pẹlu authentic ohun plus occasional clarifications. Yan ti o da lori lori akẹkọọ readiness ati kíkọ́ ibi-afẹde.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type rẹ own ṣii-ended response instead ti selecting lati pre-written ṣayan. Free response ọna promotes creative expression, critical thinking, ati authentic dialogue imọ. Responses jẹ analyzed fun historical accuracy, empathy, ati jinjin ti inquiry. Higher-quality ibeere earn sii XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Fihan tabi fipamọ response suggestions ati conversation imọran. nigba ti enabled, eto provides scaffolded ibeere starters, historical conọ̀rọ̀ prompts, ati engagement suggestions. Ìrànlọ́wọ́ful fun akẹkọọ titun si historical inquiry tabi those needing atilẹyin pẹlu ṣii-ended ìbéèrèing. olukọ le dawọ duro imọran fun sii si ti ni ilọsiwaju idanwo scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Display ìrànlọ́wọ́ful imọran fun fífani-mọ́ra pẹlu persona. imọran fikun historically relevant ibeere si ask, topics oluyaworan would find interesting, ati prompts iyẹn lead si deeper understanding. Great fun akẹkọọ who need scaffolding tabi aren't sure bawo si begin historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Firanṣẹ rẹ ifiranṣẹ si persona oluyaworan. rẹ ibeere tabi response jẹ analyzed fun relevance ati jinjin. AI persona yoo respond authentically ti o da lori lori their historical context, knowledge, ati personality. Well-crafted ibeere iyẹn fihan historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Tipa persona conversation pẹpẹ. rẹ ọrọ sisọ history ati earned XP jẹ automatically ti pamọ. iwọ le resume eyi conversation later lati History tab.",
    "persona_close_title": "Tipa Persona ọrọ sisọ",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Kọ rẹ iṣaroye lori conversation fun idanwo. Reflect lori kini iwọ learned about historical figure, bawo their perspective differs lati ìpòsírn viewpoints, ati bawo eyi conversation changed rẹ understanding. Reflections jẹ evaluated lilo rubric aligned si historical thinking imọ ati le earn significant XP.",
    "persona_conclude": "End conversation ati ṣẹda comprehensive summary ti rẹ discussion. summary pẹlu: key topics covered, historical insights gained, quality ti rẹ ibeere, empathy demonstrated, ati XP earned. eyi summary le be exported fun idanwo, added si akẹkọọ portfolios, tabi lo as writing prompt fun iṣaroye activities.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Pamọ eyi conversation si atunyẹwo tabi pin later. Fipamọ́d chats preserve pari dialogue, XP earned, timestamps, ati any iṣaroyes. Lo ti pamọ chats fun akẹkọọ portfolios, idanwo evidence, kilasi discussions, tabi exemplar ìpòsíls. Fipamọ́d conversations le be exported as PDF tabi shared pẹlu other akẹkọọ.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Get conversation starter tabi topic suggestion nigba ti iwọ're ko sure kini si ask. eto ṣẹda historically relevant ibeere ti o da lori lori persona's background, expertise, ati time period. Great fun overcoming writer's block tabi discovering titun igun si wadii ninu rẹ historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically firanṣẹ rẹ ifiranṣẹ nigba ti iwọ duro typing fun few seconds. Creates sii natural conversational flow, especially nigba ti lilo ohun dictation. Dawọ duro eyi ti o ba iwọ prefer si atunyẹwo ati ṣatunṣe ifiranṣẹ before sending, tabi ti o ba iwọ need sii time si compose thoughtful responses.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Ṣe atupale rẹ orisun ọrọ fun reading ipele, idiju, ati awọn ẹya.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "Fact-check orisun akoonu against reliable references.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Ṣẹda oju organizer lati rẹ orisun akoonu.",
    "timeline_generate_button": "Ṣẹda timeline ti events lati rẹ orisun akoonu.",
    "timeline_topic": "main topic tabi akọle ti timeline being ti ṣẹda. AI ṣẹda historically accurate events ti o da lori lori eyi topic ati rẹ orisun akoonu. apẹẹrẹ topics: American Revolution, Life Cycle ti Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events jẹ automatically ordered chronologically fun sequencing ṣe adaṣe.",
    "timeline_count": "nọmba ti events si fikun ninu timeline. sii events ṣẹda longer, sii alaye timelines ṣugbọn increase iṣoro. Recommended: 4-6 events fun beginners, 8-10 fun agbedemeji, 12+ fun si ti ni ilọsiwaju learners. Events jẹ draggable fun sequencing ṣe adaṣe after generation.",
